\b\fs28 Q-4 Name a few CSS style Components\par
\fs24 Ans: - \b0 Selector: class name, id name or element name that is target\par

\pard\widctlpar\li720\sa160\sl252\slmult1 Attribute: name of the attribute you want to style for example border, color, background, position etc.\par

