\pard\widctlpar\sa160\sl252\slmult1\b\fs28 Q-7 How can the image repetition of the backup be controlled?\par
\fs24 Ans: - \b0 This task can be achieved by using the background-repeat property that will help us to control the repetition of the image. The background-repeat property in CSS is used to repeat the background image both horizontally and vertically.\par
\b\fs28 Q-8 What is the used of the background-position properties?\par
\fs24 Ans: - \b0 The background-position property in CSS is mainly used to sets the initial position for the background image ie., it is used to set an image at a certain position.\par
\tab e.g., Syntax \endash  background-position: value;\par
\b\fs28 Q-9 Which properties controls the image scroll in the background?\par
\fs24 Ans: - \b0 The background-attachment property sets whether a background image scrolls with the rest of the page, or is fixed.\par
Syntax: - \par
\tab\cf1\highlight2 background-attachment: scroll / fixed / local / initial / inherit;\par
